BARYA(coin)

Classic jeepney drivers in the PH are the first to feel the effect of this pandemic. This piece was made last year 2020, to stand with their call for help and assistance.

-------------------------

Collecting this and other 1/1s creation means supporting a dream of the artist to continue his craft while making a living.
Join Jakestudyos on his journey and evolution.
